what you actually want, you see an endless feed of algorithmically generated outrage baits,

43:21.040 --> 43:26.540
sponsored drop-shipped products, an AI-generated slop designed purely to keep you scrolling

43:26.540 --> 43:27.560
for three more seconds.

43:27.560 --> 43:33.640
Your Omega Sub-T, your personal horizon of choice, has been artificially constrained by

43:33.640 --> 43:34.740
the platform's power.

43:35.240 --> 43:40.280
They are terraforming your preference fields, digging trenches of anger and anxiety just to

43:40.280 --> 43:41.220
